        "name": "Fluttering Distraction",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You\u2019re trained in snapping and fluttering your fans to draw the eyes of observers around you. You manipulate your fans to create a distraction. The enemy must roll its attack twice and take the lower result.",
